    tag: "Healthcare · Google Maps",
    title: "Dental Clinic, Satellite Road",
    desc: "Ranked #1 in Google Maps for 'dentist in Satellite Ahmedabad'. 3x appointment inquiries in 90 days from map pack alone.",
