    name: "Dr. Anjali Mehta",
    role: "Dental Clinic, Satellite, Ahmedabad",
  },
  {
    text: "We had no idea local SEO was this different from general SEO. DC technolabs got us into the map pack for 20 Ahmedabad searches within 4 months. Game changer for footfall.",
