  badge="📍 Local SEO Services"
  heroH1="Rank in Google Maps."
  heroHighlight="Get Found by Customers Searching Near You."
  heroDesc="Local SEO and Google Business Profile management for Ahmedabad businesses. We get you into the Google Maps top 3 for searches like 'dentist near me', 'restaurant in Satellite', and 'CA in Navrangpura'. Starting ₹25,000/month."
